data.description: Owner has filed claim for new roof due to hail/storm damage!!!  LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION!   Brick paver entry greets you as you walk up to front door, enter onto  beautiful cherry wood floor into the sunken living room highlighted by the stone wood burning fireplace.  Remodeled kitchen with granite counter tops, large island, S/S appliances, beautiful back splash. Nice area for formal or casual dining.  All bedrooms have newer vinyl plank flooring, master bathroom has double vanities, beautiful tile shower and walk in closet.  Sit back in your  screened porch with tile floor, large outdoor patio for your outdoor enjoyment.  Great house,  Great location!  By appt only.  Hurry!!  Lets make a deal
